法規內容.條文內容:
“Cultural organizations” as mentioned in Item 8 of Paragraph 2 of Article 3 of the Act means the following types of organizations established in accordance with the law:
1.	Museums and art museums;
2.	Libraries, archives, and file archives;
3.	Memorial halls, culture halls, artifact museums, and exhibition halls;
4.	Theaters, opera houses, concert halls, performance halls, and experimental theaters;
5.	Culture centers, art centers, culture and the arts centers, and art museums;
6.	Living art centers; and
7.	Other organizations concerned with culture and the arts.
